high_descs: Go toward the door and turn right to face the wooden table.
Take the gray plate from the wooden table.
Turn left, go to the door, turn left, and go to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, put the plate in the refrigerator, close the refrigerator, wait for three seconds, open the refrigerator, take the plate from the refrigerator, and close the refrigerator.
Turn around, go to the table, turn right, and go to the counter.
Open the second cabinet door, put the plate inside the cabinet, and close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled plate inside the second cabinet on the left.

high_descs: turn to the right to face the table
pick up the silver plate to the right of the white bottle from the table
turn around and move to the fridge
open the doors to the fridge, put the plate on the top shelf in the back right corner, close the doors for 8 seconds, open the doors and remove the plate and shut the doors again
turn to the left and move forward to the sink
open the right cabinet door underneath the sink and put the plate in to the cabinet and shut the door
anns.task_desc: put a chilled plate in to the cabinet

high_descs: Cross the room and walk to the large wooden table on the right.
Pick up the gray plate to the right of the white bottle in the middle of the table.
Turn left, hang a left at the wall and walk to the black fridge ahead.
Put the plate inside the fridge on the top back right corner, chill it for seven seconds, remove it, and close the doors.
Turn around and hang a right at the table to reach the cabinets under the sink.
Open the bottom right cabinet under the sink, put the chilled plate inside the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled plate in a cabinet.
